## Privacy Policy

Last updated: 5/9/2024

### Introduction
This Privacy Policy applies to the Tap Tempo app, developed to help users measure musical tempo directly on their Apple Watch.

### Information Collection and Use
The Tap Tempo app does not collect any personal data from its users. The app may collect anonymous data related to app performance and usage to help improve functionality.

### Data Storage and Security
No personal data is collected, thus no storage or specific security measures are necessary for user data.

### Data Sharing and Disclosure
No personal data is shared with third parties as none is collected. No data is disclosed to any party, except as required by law.

### User Rights
As the Tap Tempo app does not collect personal data, the rights to access, correct, delete, or transfer data are not applicable.

### Childrenâ€™s Privacy
This app is not specifically marketed to children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any information from children under 13.

### Changes to the Privacy Policy
Any changes to our Privacy Policy will be posted on this page and, where appropriate, notified to you by an update or notification.

### Contact Information
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at jonluke.jenkins@me.com
